title = "Calling Ethereum's API from Your App"

+++

First, we'd need to [install](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Building-Ethereum) Ethereum.

Once Ethereum is installed, we can start its [JSON RPC API](https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC):

```sh
geth --rpc
```

This will by default expose the RPC API on http://localhost:8545, to change the defaults:

```sh
geth --rpc --rpcaddr <ip> --rpcport <port>
```

Note that we can also start the RPC API in `geth` console:

```JavaScript
admin.startRPC('<ip>', '<port>');
```
